article.description: — Dominick Pickett and Callum McRae each recorded 12 points and 12 rebounds as UC Riverside topped UC San Diego 59-51 on Thursday night.
article.headline: Pickett, McRae lead UC Riverside past UC San Diego 59-51
article.linkText: Pickett, McRae lead UC Riverside past UC San Diego 59-51
article.story: RIVERSIDE, Calif. -- — Dominick Pickett and Callum McRae each recorded 12 points and 12 rebounds as UC Riverside topped UC San Diego 59-51 on Thursday night. Flynn Cameron had 13 points for UC Riverside (7-4, 1-0 Big West Conference), which earned its fifth consecutive home victory. JP Moorman II added 10 points and eight rebounds. Matt Gray had 11 points for the Tritons (8-6, 2-1). ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
